about other things to see in Dubai too. Lets get cracking!

#### Slow down Sam! Can you explain what the 2020 World Expo is first?

Pardon me, absolutely. Expo 2020 is the latest World Expo running from October 2021 to the end of March 2022 in Dubai, the United Arab Emirates. You can imagine the site as once of the largest museums/exhibition centers you have ever seen. Comprising of 192 Country Pavillions, 5 Central Pavillions and a host of other themed Pavillions; the Expo 2020 site covers 4.4km<sup>2</sup> of what was desert only 5 years previously (see images below). The logistical challenge alone to build a site of this scale, variation and complexity in such a short space of time is mind boggling.

