Inside each pavillion the host aims to showcase their technology, history and culture. This can take many forms, from artwork to artificial intelligence. Many pavillions also aim to focus on one of three major themes covered at Expo 2020 Dubai: Mobility, Sustainability and Opportunity. A brief outline of these themes is as follows:

* **Mobility** - Developments surrounding technological and social mobility. This can come in many forms including data mobility, public and private transport, open education and technology for equity among many others.
* **Sustainability** - Developments surrounding sustainable causes. For example: renewable energies, sustainabile architecture, energy monitoring, sustainable policy and sustainability education to name a few.
* **Opportunity** - Stories, technologies, information and inspiration surrounding the United Nations (UN) Sustainabile Development Goals (SDGs).